{"word":"H2498 - חלף - châlaph - khaw-laf'","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: חלף"},{"paragraph":"Transliteration: châlaph"},{"paragraph":"Phonetic: khaw-laf'"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உருவக்கடாவு. கடந்துபோ, முளை, ஒழி, மாறு, விடி, மாற்று, புதிதாக்கு, செலுத்து, தழை, மாறுபாடாக்கு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to pass on or away, to pass through, to pass by, to go through, to grow up, to change, to go on from"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal)"},{"paragraph":"1) to pass on quickly"},{"paragraph":"2) to pass away (vanish)"},{"paragraph":"3) to come on anew, to sprout again (of grass)"},{"paragraph":"4) to pass through"},{"paragraph":"5) to overstep, to transgress"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel) to cause to pass, to change"},{"paragraph":"c) (Hiph)"},{"paragraph":"1) to change, to substitute, to alter, to change for better, to renew"},{"paragraph":"2) to show newness (used of a tree)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Cognate: <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2475 - חלוף - chălôph - khal-ofe'/2475\">H2475</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2487 - חליפה - chălı̂yphâh - khal-ee-faw'/2487\">H2487</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2498 - חלף - châlaph - khaw-laf'/2498\">H2498</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2500 - חלף - chêleph - klay'-lef/2500\">H2500</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H2501 - חלף - cheleph - kheh'lef/2501\">H2501</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H4252 - מחלף - machălâph - makh-al-awf'/4252\">H4252</a>, <a href=\"https://wordofgod.in/bibledictionary/ஸ்ட்ராங்க்ஸ்-எபிரேய-அகராதி/#/H4253 - מחלפה - machlâphâh - makh-law-faw'/4253\">H4253</a>"}]}